    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要绘制一个用户购物旅程图，从浏览到最终收货的完整流程。整体分为三个阶段：浏览、购买和售后。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Browse",
        "Purchase",
        "Post-Purchase"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个阶段。浏览阶段我想确认一下，用户是从访问首页开始的吗？然后搜索商品、查看详情？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit homepage",
        "Search products",
        "View product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。访问首页的体验最好，给5分；搜索和查看商品都是4分，稍微复杂一点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit homepage: 5",
        "Search products: 4",
        "View product: 4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，浏览阶段已添加。接下来是购买阶段：加入购物车、填写信息、支付，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Add to cart",
        "Enter details",
        "Make payment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，但支付环节需要标注一下，这里涉及支付网关，不是用户单独完成的。而且支付体验最差，只有1分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make payment: 1: User, Payment Gateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，支付环节已加上支付网关。那售后阶段呢？确认订单、物流跟踪、收货？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Confirmation",
        "Track order",
        "Receive product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认订单这里要注意，是系统自动发送的，需要标注系统和用户双方。确认和收货都是5分，物流跟踪4分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Confirmation: 5: User, System",
        "Track order: 4",
        "Receive product: 5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
